title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Mar 31 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Mar 31 2022
description:
Why now? Media suddenly reports Hunter Biden story. Kamala's latest word salad, translated. Rep. Jim Jordan hangs out with Clay and Buck, vows to investigate the tech giants for covering up the Hunter Biden story, says GOP congress will introduce anti-trust legislation, weighs in on the "why now?" question and Clay and Buck's steak dinner bet. Clay takes heat for TV outfits, including from Mrs. Travis.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
